1
00:00:13,510 --> 00:00:15,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My first time back home in a year!</i></font>

2
00:00:16,230 --> 00:00:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father, Mother.</font>

3
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've completed my year of bridal 
training and returned home.</font>

4
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home, Tiara.</font>

5
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy to be home, Mother!</font>

6
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll have to tell us all 
about Marinforest.</font>

7
00:00:32,530 --> 00:00:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

8
00:00:34,030 --> 00:00:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hear about all that's 
happened here in the past year, too.</font>

9
00:00:40,870 --> 00:00:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought some delicious wine.</font>

10
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we all enjoy it together?</font>

11
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much, Prince Aquasteed.</font>

12
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Pardon me, sir, 
but visitors have arrived.</font>

13
00:00:55,730 --> 00:00:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Visitors? But I wasn't expecting anyone.</font>

14
00:00:59,160 --> 00:01:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

15
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Prince Hartknights and Lady Akari.</font>

16
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What are those two doing here?</i></font>

17
00:01:24,650 --> 00:01:29,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an2}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="28"><b><font color="#f76bb3">The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
<font color="#6b3e34">by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

18
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><b><font color="#f76bb3"><font size="25">Blessings</font></font></b> <font color="#6b3e34">on the <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Teary Bride</b></font></font></font></font>

19
00:02:49,410 --> 00:02:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send them away at once!</font>

20
00:02:52,610 --> 00:02:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father, I want to speak with Lady Akari.</font>

21
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara...</font>

22
00:02:59,070 --> 00:03:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking, Lady Tiararose?!</font>

23
00:03:02,900 --> 00:03:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't blame them all for being angry.</i></font>

24
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you lose to the sequel's heroine, 
I'll never forgive you!</i></font>

25
00:03:11,780 --> 00:03:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just Lady Akari alone will do.</font>

26
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

27
00:03:15,170 --> 00:03:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, Father.</font>

28
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I knew who you got 
your stubbornness from.</font>

29
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will allow it,</font>

30
00:03:23,930 --> 00:03:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but only under the condition that 
Prince Aquasteed accompanies you.</font>

31
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then, shall we?</font>

32
00:03:29,970 --> 00:03:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for being so demanding.</font>

33
00:03:32,940 --> 00:03:37,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. 
I love listening to your demands.</font>

34
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Lady Tiara! Long time no see!</font>

35
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and Prince Aqua is here as well.</font>

36
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to see you again. 
I'm so glad you seem well.</font>

37
00:03:48,790 --> 00:03:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's been a long time.</font>

38
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to see you again.</font>

39
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy to see you're 
doing well, Lady Akari.</font>

40
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! I'm working hard 
with Prince Hartknights!</font>

41
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we're long past the ending, 
I feel like I'm playing the next new game!</font>

42
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sh-She hasn't changed, I see...</i></font>

43
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops! How silly of me!</font>

44
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiara, Prince Aqua, allow me 
to congratulate you on your marriage.</font>

45
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Lady Akari.</font>

46
00:04:18,990 --> 00:04:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

47
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can see it.</i></font>

48
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well done winning out 
over the sequel's heroine!</i></font>

49
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can just tell she's thinking that!</i></font>

50
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you had any trouble this past year?</font>

51
00:04:32,450 --> 00:04:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weren't bullied, were you?</font>

52
00:04:34,370 --> 00:04:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the sea fairies, especially!</font>

53
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, they don't like me.</font>

54
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?! I knew that was 
how it would turn out!</font>

55
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I brought these 
as your wedding gifts!</font>

56
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Earrings?</font>

57
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

58
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've only ever had 
the clasping kind before, right?</font>

59
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I made these!</font>

60
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're protective charms 
that I added the Holy Prayer to!</font>

61
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are protective charms?</font>

62
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One is the pink color of my hair,</font>

63
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the other is the dark 
blue of Prince Aqua's hair.</font>

64
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to wear something,</font>

65
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it should be the color 
of the one you love!</font>

66
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I wear this!</font>

67
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yellow is...</i></font>

68
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although things are still 
a bit awkward between us...</font>

69
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Prince Hartknights 
has been so adorable lately!</font>

70
00:05:22,300 --> 00:05:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He came along with me, 
saying he wanted to see you!</font>

71
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Lady Akari.</font>

72
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome!</font>

73
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I've received this gift, 
I'd like to put them on.</font>

74
00:05:33,410 --> 00:05:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to put them on, I don't mind.</font>

75
00:05:36,570 --> 00:05:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm more surprised to see you 
being so friendly with Lady Akari.</font>

76
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You have a point. 
She did attack me, after all.</font>

77
00:05:47,790 --> 00:05:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now we're basically partners 
in taking down the sequel's heroine!</font>

78
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heroine?</font>

79
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara?</font>

80
00:05:56,010 --> 00:05:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry.</font>

81
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were there to save me 
when that happened, after all.</font>

82
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly... You'd better 
tell me the truth one day.</font>

83
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

84
00:06:07,930 --> 00:06:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's clear to me</font>

85
00:06:09,150 --> 00:06:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that you've been holding on to 
something you can't tell me.</font>

86
00:06:12,210 --> 00:06:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

87
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if you keep me in the dark for too long, 
be prepared for the consequences.</font>

88
00:06:20,210 --> 00:06:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine to be all flirty, but do it 
when I'm not around, please.</font>

89
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

90
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's all right.</font>

91
00:06:28,650 --> 00:06:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just make sure you find happiness!</font>

92
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

93
00:06:45,970 --> 00:06:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father, Mother, I am truly happy.</font>

94
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara...</font>

95
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father raised me strictly,</font>

96
00:06:55,610 --> 00:07:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and my mother helped me 
experience many things.</font>

97
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And all of that gives me strength now.</font>

98
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:08,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. We're so glad to see you this happy.</font>

99
00:07:18,990 --> 00:07:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next time we meet will be 
at your wedding in Marinforest.</font>

100
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so excited to see you 
in your bridal attire.</font>

101
00:07:26,590 --> 00:07:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

102
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow's the day I finally 
become Prince Aqua's wife.</i></font>

103
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:45,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look beautiful, Lady Tiararose.</font>

104
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you've safely arrived at your 
wedding day with Prince Aquasteed!</font>

105
00:07:51,070 --> 00:07:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really now, Philine.</font>

106
00:07:53,710 --> 00:07:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the use in crying now?</font>

107
00:07:56,330 --> 00:07:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wedding is tomorrow.</font>

108
00:07:58,470 --> 00:08:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. I'm just so excited, 
I couldn't help it.</font>

109
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who could that be? 
We weren't expecting anyone, were we?</font>

110
00:08:08,650 --> 00:08:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I'll go see.</font>

111
00:08:14,850 --> 00:08:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not going to get a visit</i></font>

112
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>from Lady Icilla, the heroine, 
the day before my wedding, am I?</i></font>

113
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Lady Icilla.</font>

114
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to visit when you're so busy.</font>

115
00:08:31,570 --> 00:08:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I'm very happy 
you came to see me.</font>

116
00:08:37,330 --> 00:08:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on your wedding.</font>

117
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just had to tell you that.</font>

118
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

119
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She didn't come to stop the wedding?</i></font>

120
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I expected her to be in love 
with Prince Aqua, but...</i></font>

121
00:08:54,360 --> 00:09:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you, perhaps, think that I had 
feelings for Prince Aquasteed?</font>

122
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:06,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand love very well.</font>

123
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always believed that my father 
would find me a good man to marry.</font>

124
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She doesn't understand love?</i></font>

125
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could that be because I exist?</i></font>

126
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Originally, Lady Icilla was supposed to</i></font>

127
00:09:19,650 --> 00:09:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>nurture her love with Prince Aqua, 
one of the conquerable routes.</i></font>

128
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If not for me, they should 
have ended up together.</i></font>

129
00:09:30,130 --> 00:09:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It wouldn't be right 
to apologize now, but...</i></font>

130
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla, I...</font>

131
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right there.</font>

132
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Akari?!</font>

133
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once again, congratulations 
on your marriage!</font>

134
00:09:47,650 --> 00:09:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pleasure to meet you, Lady Icilla.</font>

135
00:09:50,050 --> 00:09:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Akari.</font>

136
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for greeting me, Lady Akari.</font>

137
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Icilla Pearllant.</font>

138
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sequel's heroine...</font>

139
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep, just like in the game.</font>

140
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:07,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should be happier. 
You got to be the heroine, after all.</font>

141
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

142
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Akari, please 
don't be rude to Lady Icilla!</font>

143
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! I'm sorry!</font>

144
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:18,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I upset you? I apologize.</font>

145
00:10:18,610 --> 00:10:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, it didn't bother me at all.</font>

146
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Akari, why are you here?</font>

147
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to see the lucky girl 
who got to be the sequel's heroine.</font>

148
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:31,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, life ought to be enjoyed!</font>

149
00:10:31,530 --> 00:10:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla's the heroine, 
but she's not enjoying it at all!</font>

150
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose this is better than losing 
Prince Aqua to her, though.</font>

151
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really do love otome games, don't you?</font>

152
00:10:41,010 --> 00:10:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two seem to be very good friends.</font>

153
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

154
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! That's exactly right! 
I'm Lady Tiara's friend!</font>

155
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm so worried about her!</font>

156
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Worried?</font>

157
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Because you're always 
hanging around Prince Aqua!</font>

158
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better not get too close 
to my friend's husband!</font>

159
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:06,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Akari, what are you...</font>

160
00:11:07,490 --> 00:11:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry, Lady Tiararose.</font>

161
00:11:10,340 --> 00:11:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true. I should have been 
more considerate.</font>

162
00:11:14,570 --> 00:11:16,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't say that, Lady Icilla.</font>

163
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to worry 
about that at all.</font>

164
00:11:20,060 --> 00:11:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Lady Akari, 
stop saying things like that!</font>

165
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

166
00:11:26,650 --> 00:11:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, Lady Tiararose.</font>

167
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed will be arriving soon.</font>

168
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

169
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for staying so long.</font>

170
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take my leave now.</font>

171
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A dark blue ribbon...</i></font>

172
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of the sequel's heroine. 
She's such a sweet girl.</font>

173
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Akari, did you come here 
to say something to Lady Icilla?</font>

174
00:11:56,960 --> 00:12:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really. I only came to see 
how the sequel ends.</font>

175
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:04,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How it ends? What do you mean by that?</font>

176
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, bye!</font>

177
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Akari?!</font>

178
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

179
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better not get too close 
to my friend's husband!</font>

180
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never meant to do that.</i></font>

181
00:12:46,230 --> 00:12:51,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have any romantic feelings 
for Prince Aquasteed at all.</i></font>

182
00:12:52,300 --> 00:12:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Highness is so brilliant and mature.</i></font>

183
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's completely out of my reach...</i></font>

184
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sure I don't look strange?</font>

185
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the most beautiful thing 
in the world! Be more confident!</font>

186
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

187
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not really. I only came to see 
how the sequel ends.</i></font>

188
00:13:36,990 --> 00:13:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did she mean some kind of event 
is going to happen during the wedding?</i></font>

189
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is an otome game world, after all.</i></font>

190
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way nothing's 
going to happen at a wedding.</i></font>

191
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for you to make your entrance.</font>

192
00:14:38,210 --> 00:14:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why... does my heart hurt so much?</i></font>

193
00:14:42,650 --> 00:14:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not as if I was in love 
with Prince Aquasteed, so why...</i></font>

194
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did I actually love him after all?</i></font>

195
00:14:55,690 --> 00:14:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was this feeling I had for him 
more than just respect?</i></font>

196
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aquasteed!</i></font>

197
00:15:07,050 --> 00:15:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you do it.</font>

198
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was I...</font>

199
00:15:11,650 --> 00:15:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla, you really do love 
Prince Aquasteed, don't you?</font>

200
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... I...</font>

201
00:15:19,170 --> 00:15:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would never...</font>

202
00:15:23,830 --> 00:15:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... are you telling me 
this pain in my chest... is love?</font>

203
00:15:30,610 --> 00:15:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, I figured this event would happen.</i></font>

204
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The sequel game has an event where the 
romantic interest marries someone else,</i></font>

205
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the heroine can intervene and stop it.</i></font>

206
00:15:44,330 --> 00:15:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The unlock condition</i></font>

207
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is wearing a ribbon in your love 
interest's color to the wedding.</i></font>

208
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, I love those 
"intervening in the wedding" events.</font>

209
00:15:58,380 --> 00:16:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They get your heart racing, you know?</font>

210
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because the groom 
chooses you over his bride.</font>

211
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But more than that,</font>

212
00:16:07,450 --> 00:16:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't allow anyone to ruin my friend's 
wedding when she's smiling so happily.</font>

213
00:16:12,930 --> 00:16:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a coincidence. I agree with you.</font>

214
00:16:16,490 --> 00:16:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keith, the Forest Fairy King?!</font>

215
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla, was it?</font>

216
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you try to do anything 
to those two, I won't let it slide.</font>

217
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I would never do such a thing!</font>

218
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will do as you wish, Fairy King.</font>

219
00:16:41,190 --> 00:16:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess I really can't be by 
Prince Aquasteed's side, can I?</i></font>

220
00:16:50,950 --> 00:16:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hear someone crying.</i></font>

221
00:16:55,810 --> 00:17:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was right. Lady Icilla 
really did love Prince Aqua.</i></font>

222
00:17:06,360 --> 00:17:07,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>N-No!</i></font>

223
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been so scared about whether 
this wedding would actually happen.</i></font>

224
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I kept asking what I'd do if Prince Aqua 
chose Lady Icilla at the last moment.</i></font>

225
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But even if I am standing in the way 
of what should be their true love...</i></font>

226
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, I...</i></font>

227
00:17:37,950 --> 00:17:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua!</font>

228
00:17:41,970 --> 00:17:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua!</font>

229
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Losing isn't an option! 
I love Prince Aqua more than anyone!</i></font>

230
00:17:50,630 --> 00:17:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be with him forever!</i></font>

231
00:17:55,170 --> 00:17:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara...</font>

232
00:17:57,510 --> 00:18:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see I've made you feel uneasy again.</font>

233
00:18:10,730 --> 00:18:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Prince Aqua...</font>

234
00:18:22,020 --> 00:18:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed?</font>

235
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for attending 
our wedding today.</font>

236
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. Congratulations, 
Prince Aquasteed... Lady Tiararose.</font>

237
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiararose is the one most precious to me.</font>

238
00:18:46,450 --> 00:18:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Lady Icilla.</font>

239
00:18:50,970 --> 00:18:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

240
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did admire you, Prince Aquasteed.</font>

241
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've moved past it now.</font>

242
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please go on to be happier 
than anyone in the world.</font>

243
00:19:07,410 --> 00:19:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And thank you for teaching me 
what love feels like.</font>

244
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, honestly...</font>

245
00:19:13,670 --> 00:19:17,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so cute when you cry, 
I just want to eat you up.</font>

246
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you stopped.</font>

247
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, this ring is filled with my magic.</font>

248
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you accept it?</font>

249
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, Prince Aqua.</font>

250
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, I will hold on to you forever.</font>

251
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will hold on to you forever, too.</font>

252
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do.</font>

253
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara...</font>

254
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you.</font>

255
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll treasure you for life 
and make you happy.</font>

256
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I love you, too.</font>

257
00:20:16,970 --> 00:20:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It looks like stars raining down...</i></font>

258
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To the next king and his queen!</font>

259
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have my blessing 
for your health and happiness,</font>

260
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:27,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and for peace in this kingdom!</font>

261
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keith!</font>

262
00:20:29,020 --> 00:20:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fairy King!</font>

263
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Forest Fairy King 
blessed them! Amazing!</font>

264
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a joyous occasion!</font>

265
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose! Prince Aquasteed!</font>

266
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:53,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations!</font>

267
00:20:53,120 --> 00:20:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations!</font>

268
00:20:55,110 --> 00:20:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blast it all. Tiara looks so lovely 
when she commands the flowers.</font>

269
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's troubling how much 
it makes me want her.</font>

270
00:21:00,530 --> 00:21:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll make Prince Aqua 
angry talking like that.</font>

271
00:21:18,610 --> 00:21:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you crying again, Tiara?</font>

272
00:21:21,260 --> 00:21:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, goodness. Silly me.</font>

273
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just so happy and blessed, 
my tears won't stop flowing.</font>

274
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy, too.</font>

275
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now the game is over.</i></font>

276
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From this point on, 
I'll truly live in reality.</i></font>

277
00:21:40,690 --> 00:21:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No more living at the mercy of a game.</i></font>

278
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love is worthless.</font>

279
00:23:30,010 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc">A <font color="#f76bb3"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Like <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Ripples</b> <font color="#6b3e34">on the Water</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

280
00:23:30,010 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#6b3e34">A <font color="#f76bb3"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Like <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Ripples</b> <font color="#6b3e34">on the Water</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

281
00:23:30,730 --> 00:23:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My love will never be realized.</font>

282
00:23:33,420 --> 00:23:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to sink it 
into the depths of the sea.</font>

283
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... when I see him smile, I...</font>

